n<ul>\n<li>\u1ea4m tr\u00e0 t\u1eed sa<\/li>\n<li>B\u1ed9 d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee5 g\u1eafp<\/li>\n<li>B\u1ed9 tr\u00e0 g\u1ed7 h\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u00e9n qu\u00e2n<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u00e9n t\u1ed1ng<\/li>\n<li>D\u1ee5ng c\u1ee5 tr\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1o<\/li>\n<li>Khay tr\u00e0<\/li>\n<li>L\u1ecdc tr\u00e0<\/li>\n<li>V\u1eadt ph\u1ea9m phong th\u1ee7y<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1780 size-full lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/haitra.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Ch%E1%BA%A5t-l%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-HaiTra.vn-mang-t%E1%BB%9Bi-gi%C3%A1-tr%E1%BB%8B-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-t%E1%BB%93n.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 830px) 100vw, 830px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/haitra.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Ch\u1ea5t-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-HaiTra.vn-mang-t\u1edbi-gi\u00e1-tr\u1ecb-tr\u01b0\u1eddng-t\u1ed3n.jpg 830w, https:\/\/haitra.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Ch\u1ea5t-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-HaiTra.vn-mang-t\u1edbi-gi\u00e1-tr\u1ecb-tr\u01b0\u1eddng-t\u1ed3n-300x181.jpg 300w, https:\/\/haitra.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Ch\u1ea5t-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-HaiTra.vn-mang-t\u1edbi-gi\u00e1-tr\u1ecb-tr\u01b0\u1eddng-t\u1ed3n-768x463.jpg 768w, https:\/\/haitra.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Ch\u1ea5t-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-HaiTra.vn-mang-t\u1edbi-gi\u00e1-tr\u1ecb-tr\u01b0\u1eddng-t\u1ed3n-600x361.jpg 600w\" alt=\"Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mang t\u1edbi c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ed3n\" width=\"830\" height=\"500\" data-src=\"https:\/\/haitra.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Ch\u1ea5t-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-HaiTra.vn-mang-t\u1edbi-gi\u00e1-tr\u1ecb-tr\u01b0\u1eddng-t\u1ed3n.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/haitra.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Ch\u1ea5t-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-HaiTra.vn-mang-t\u1edbi-gi\u00e1-tr\u1ecb-tr\u01b0\u1eddng-t\u1ed3n.jpg 830w, https:\/\/haitra.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Ch\u1ea5t-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-HaiTra.vn-mang-t\u1edbi-gi\u00e1-tr\u1ecb-tr\u01b0\u1eddng-t\u1ed3n-300x181.jpg 300w, https